import React from "react"
import { Text, TouchableOpacity, View } from "react-native"
export const DrawerContent = (props) => {
    return (
        <View style={{
            flex : 1,
            paddingTop : 45,
        }}>
            <View style={{width : "100%", paddingLeft : 30, paddingTop : 20, marginBottom : 20}}>
                <Text style={{fontSize : 40, fontWeight : '700'}}>Profile</Text>
                <Text style={{fontSize : 16, fontWeight : '400', color : 'lightgray'}}>@แกะนิรนาม</Text>
            </View>
            <View style={{width : '100%', borderBottomWidth : 1,
                          borderBottomColor : 'lightgray'}} />
            <View style={{width : "100%", paddingLeft : 30, paddingTop : 20}}>
                <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => {props.navigation.navigate("Home")}} 
                    style={{marginBottom : 20}}>
                    <Text>Home</Text>
                </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
            <View style={{width : '100%', borderBottomWidth : 1,
                          borderBottomColor : 'lightgray'}} />
            <View style={{width : '100%', paddingLeft : 30, paddingTop : 20}}>
                <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => {props.navigation.navigate("Login")}} 
                style={{marginBottom : 20}}>
                    <Text>Log In</Text>
                </TouchableOpacity>
                <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => {props.navigation.navigate("SignUp")}} 
                style={{}}>
                    <Text>Sign Up</Text>
                </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
}
